      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SCOTT SIGMA (7) jumped from the inside and boxed on well to finish second last time, beaten one length (29.69) behind Lamia Nonna Mim at this track. Can go on with it. HI BIG BEN (4) crossed over from out wide last start before finishing third (30.05) at this track in a Grade 5 over 515m. Hard to beat again. BOMB OVER (6) doesn't have the best strike-rate but recent form is sound. Has been in the money the last three starts, the latest when third (29.75) at this track. Has a good record at this journey. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings two times from three starts. Expected to be in the finish again. PAW STELLA (8) generally performs well from this box.",
